(87,'DELL',46785,'This Dell model features 8GB RAM and 256GB ROM, providing solid performance for everyday users. Best suited for browsing, documents, light entertainment, and office usage. Built with Dell’s signature durability, smooth display quality, and long battery backup for all‑day usage.','Laptop','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81ImBTVkbmL._AC_UY218_.jpg'),
