(45,'RedMi',36000,'A budget‑friendly yet capable Redmi smartphone offering 12GB RAM and 256GB ROM. Ideal for gaming, streaming, social media, and daily communication. Features a vibrant display, long battery life, and optimized software for smooth everyday usage. A great value pick for performance‑oriented users.','Mobile','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81dblfYZOYL._AC_UL320_.jpg'),
