(67,'Samsung',31000,'A feature‑rich Samsung smartphone with 12GB RAM and 256GB ROM, offering a premium display, smooth UI, strong cameras, and all‑day battery backup. Excellent for gaming, streaming, office apps, and photography. Ideal for users who prefer dependable, polished performance.','Mobile','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71EeBkydf9L._AC_UL320_.jpg'),
