(34,'Apple 15 Pro',65000,'The Apple 15 Pro offers elegance and top‑notch performance with 12GB RAM and 256GB ROM. Delivers a premium camera setup, fluid display, excellent security, and a long lifespan. Perfect for creatives, business users, and anyone seeking a luxury mobile experience.','Mobile','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/616-Eh2FbPL._AC_UY218_.jpg'),
